stories.text:
I'm trying to find any record of it. I used to read it a ton as a teenager... it was one of the first "news" websites I ever found. Archive.org isn't helping...nothing at salvo.com but I'm not even sure that was the address. This would have been around 1994-95... it was kind of an anarchist / foreign policy zine if I remember. Not the current Christian fundamentalist magazine called "Salvo" at salvomag.com, which seems to have been around since 2006 (although the new one has really funny headlines like "How Pornography and Drugs Changes your Brain" [sic]).

Anyone got a recollection or a copy of what I'm talking about?
